description: People returning from these countries to the Republic will not have to restrict their movements.
title: Republic of Ireland adds 15 countries to travel 'green list'
title_page: Republic of Ireland adds 15 countries to travel 'green list' - BBC News
maintext: In a statement the Irish government said: "Anyone arriving into Ireland from these countries will not have to restrict their movements. Passengers from any other country outside of those with a Normal Precautions advisory are asked to restrict their movements for 14 days."
